item.title: CVE-2023-46656|2024-08-02T20:53:21.182Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20multibranch%20scan%20webhook%20trigger%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Multibranch Scan Webhook Trigger Plugin 1.0.9 and earlier uses a non-constant time comparison function when checking whether the provided and expected webhook token are equal, potentially allowing attackers to use statistical methods to obtain a valid webhook token.
